nl.strohalm.cyclos.services.stats.taxes

Class TransferVolumePerMemberStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.strohalm.cyclos.services.stats.taxes.TransferVolumePerMemberStats
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GrossProductPerMemberStats, TaxesPerMemberStats

    public abstract class TransferVolumePerMemberStats
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines common helper methods for retrieving stats on transfer volume per member. These may be incoming transfers (Gross Product for Activity Stats) or outgoing transfers (Payments, for Taxes Stats). Subsequent subclasses divide between those two.
    Author:
    rinke
